room_title: Escape room "C-Block" by Escape Experience - Nashville Escape Games in Nashville
review: The attention to detail and creativity of C-Block is second to none. The Escape Experience is close to TPAC and a short walk from Broadway, so there's a lot of entertainment close by to enjoy (if you managed to escape).Highly recommended!

room_title: Escape room "C-Block" by Escape Experience - Nashville Escape Games in Nashville
review: Just completed the escape from Cell Block C. Erin was our game-master and she was awesome! The clues were well laid out and Erin's clutch assistance came at just the right times. We did this event as a team building event and loved it.
